      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "RN"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "pgm/dcp/fls/ioc/obj/iofzls"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-zls                 .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se At end : ad uscita                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to loa-tbl-zls-900.
       loa-tbl-zls-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
