      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        rf-lsd-cod-lst       not  = w-sto-lst-cod-lst
                     go to sto-prz-lst-590.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Codice cliente                          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        rf-lsd-cod-cli       not  = w-sto-lst-cod-cli
                     go to sto-prz-lst-590.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
