      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        rf-lsd-sgl-vlt       not  = w-sto-lst-sgl-vlt
                     go to sto-prz-lst-590.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Numero decimali valuta                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        rf-lsd-dec-vlt       not  = w-sto-lst-dec-vlt
                     go to sto-prz-lst-590.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Codice prodotto, numerico               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        rf-lsd-num-pro       not  = w-sto-lst-num-pro
                     go to sto-prz-lst-590.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
