                     w-sto-lst-flg-del    not  = "S"
                     go to sto-prz-lst-680.
       sto-prz-lst-677.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Incremento                              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-sto-lst-ctr-apd      .
