           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "<"                  to   v-edm                  .
           move      21                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      69                   to   v-pos                  .
           move      w-sto-lst-ctr-apd    to   v-num                  .
